## Boss Tool Restrictions from on-pre-tool-use.sh

### Restriction 1: send-keys ŌĆö Boss can ONLY send-keys to Taskmaster pane (lines 551-568)

```bash
# Line 551-568
if [ "$_DOEY_ROLE" = "$DOEY_ROLE_ID_BOSS" ] && [ "$TOOL_NAME" = "Bash" ]; then
  _BOSS_CMD="$_BASH_CMD"
  _boss_tm_pane="${DOEY_TASKMASTER_PANE:-1.0}"
  _boss_tm_safe=$(echo "$_boss_tm_pane" | tr '.' '_')
  case "$_BOSS_CMD" in *"send-keys"*"-t"*)
    _boss_target=$(echo "$_BOSS_CMD" | sed 's/.*send-keys[[:space:]]*-t[[:space:]]*//;s/[[:space:]].*//;s/^"//;s/"$//')
    case "$_boss_target" in
      *:${_boss_tm_pane}|*_${_boss_tm_safe}*|${_boss_tm_pane})
        _dbg_write "allow_boss_sendkeys_coordinator"
        ;; # fall through to boss exit 0
      *)
        _log_block "TOOL_BLOCKED" "Boss send-keys to non-Taskmaster pane blocked" "$_BOSS_CMD"
        _dbg_write "block_boss_sendkeys_${_boss_target}"
        _forward_action "Bash" "$_BOSS_CMD" "send-keys relay" || true
        echo "FORWARDED: Command relay request sent to Taskmaster." >&2
        exit 2 ;;  # BLOCKED with feedback
    esac
  ;; esac
```

**Summary:** Boss send-keys to Taskmaster pane (1.0) = ALLOWED. Boss send-keys to any other pane = BLOCKED (exit 2) and forwarded to Taskmaster.

### Restriction 2: capture-pane ŌĆö Boss can capture ANY pane (lines 570-573)

```bash
# Line 570-573
  case "$_BOSS_CMD" in *"capture-pane"*)
    _dbg_write "allow_boss_capturepane"
    ;; # fall through to boss exit 0
  esac
fi
```

**Summary:** capture-pane is always allowed for Boss (read-only observation).

### Restriction 3: Read/Edit/Write/Glob/Grep ŌĆö Boss blocked on project source files (lines 598-756)

```bash
# Line 598
if { [ "$_DOEY_ROLE" = "$DOEY_ROLE_ID_BOSS" ] || [ "$_DOEY_ROLE" = "$DOEY_ROLE_ID_TEAM_LEAD" ] || [ "$_DOEY_ROLE" = "$DOEY_ROLE_ID_COORDINATOR" ]; } && [ "$TOOL_NAME" != "Bash" ]; then
  case "$TOOL_NAME" in
    Agent)
      # ... blocked, forwarded to Taskmaster (exit 2)
    Read|Edit|Write|Glob|Grep)
      _CHK_PATH=$(_json_str tool_input.file_path)
      [ -z "$_CHK_PATH" ] && _CHK_PATH=$(_json_str tool_input.path)
      [ "$_DOEY_ROLE" = "$DOEY_ROLE_ID_BOSS" ] && [ -z "$_CHK_PATH" ] && _CHK_PATH=$(_json_str tool_input.pattern)
```

**Exceptions (ALLOWED for Boss):**
- **Image files** (line 616-621): Boss can Read `.png`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg`, `.gif`, `.webp`, `.svg`, `.bmp`, `.ico`, `.pdf` at any path
- **Task files** (line 623+): `.doey/tasks/*` paths are allowed
- **Runtime/scratchpad paths**: `$RUNTIME_DIR/*`, `$DOEY_SCRATCHPAD` are allowed (scratchpad bypass at line 576)

**Everything else:** BLOCKED. Boss cannot Read/Edit/Write/Glob/Grep project source files.

