## Boss Tool Restriction Summary Table

| Tool | Boss Access | Condition |
|------|------------|-----------|
| `send-keys` (Bash) | PARTIAL | Only to Taskmaster pane (1.0). All others BLOCKED + forwarded |
| `capture-pane` (Bash) | ALLOWED | All panes (read-only observation) |
| `Read` | PARTIAL | Image files at any path = ALLOWED. `.doey/tasks/*`, runtime, scratchpad = ALLOWED. Project source = BLOCKED |
| `Edit` | PARTIAL | `.doey/tasks/*`, runtime, scratchpad = ALLOWED. Project source = BLOCKED |
| `Write` | PARTIAL | `.doey/tasks/*`, runtime, scratchpad = ALLOWED. Project source = BLOCKED |
| `Glob` | PARTIAL | `.doey/tasks/*`, runtime, scratchpad = ALLOWED. Project source = BLOCKED |
| `Grep` | PARTIAL | `.doey/tasks/*`, runtime, scratchpad = ALLOWED. Project source = BLOCKED |
| `Agent` | BLOCKED | Always. Forwarded to Taskmaster |
| `AskUserQuestion` | EXCLUSIVE | Only Boss can use it. All other roles' questions forwarded to Boss |
| `Bash` (general) | ALLOWED | Catch-all allows after specific checks pass |

