## CRITICAL FINDING: Working Copy Empty

The working copy of `agents/doey-boss.md` is **0 bytes**. This means the Boss agent currently has NO instructions loaded. The template (`doey-boss.md.tmpl`) and git HEAD are intact. Running `bash shell/expand-templates.sh` would regenerate the file from the template.
